      <p>
         To compile you can use the xmlBlaster/src/c++/tao.xml file.
      </p>
      <p>
         Please take a copy from xmlBlaster/build.properties into
         your home directory (it has precedence there) and adjust
         the path settings to find CORBA and the XML parser.
      </p>
      <p>
         Compile it with ant:
      </p>
      <pre>
cd xmlBlaster\src\c++
..\..\build.bat -verbose -f tao.xml all

This creates:
   xmlBlaster\src\c++\tao_build\xmlBlasterClient.dll
      </pre>
   </configuration>

